Attribution
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

prism is a derivative work — a major rework — of "paper-reader", a community
Claude Code skill distributed in a Chinese ML-research skill pack. The original
author of paper-reader is unknown.

Reused from paper-reader (reworked and extended):
  - Zotero integration patterns
  - the Obsidian concept-library framework
  - the paper-note template
  - the multi-source figure fallback strategy

If you recognize paper-reader, or you are its author, please open an issue at
https://github.com/yangjc27/prism/issues so we can credit you properly and link
back to the original.

paper-reader's original license was not distributed with the skill pack we
found it in. prism is released under MIT in good faith; should the original
author come forward with different terms, we will reconcile attribution and
licensing accordingly.
